# Git commit messages

When creating git commits in this project:

- **Never** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any Cursor co-author trailer.
- **Never** add `Co-authored-by:` lines for the AI agent or Cursor.
- Write commit messages as the developer only — short subject, optional body, no agent attribution footers.
- If a tool or template suggests adding a Co-authored-by line, omit it.
